"{\"uid\": \"perthnow.com.au-news-offbeat-athlete-reveals-contents-of-paris-olympic-village-welcome-back-featuring-condoms-and-smartphone-c-15489037\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Get the FREE App  Get the FREE App  Canadian sailor Sarah Douglas has gone viral after providing a sneak peek into the welcome packs gifted to athletes in the ParisOlympicvillage.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9502353126084118, \"rank\": 0.04126650197575953, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 52, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Douglas_(actress)\", \"score\": 0.9991919721321767, \"rank\": 0.0008082440897150714, \"text\": \"Sarah Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Douglas_(actress)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Douglas_(actress)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sharing a video toTikTok, the 30-year-old offered a mini-tour of her room - featuring the infamous cardboard single beds thought to deter morale-boosting under the sheets.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time Olympian began the clip with the caption, \\\"What every Olympic athlete receives in their room\\\", and continued to provide a close-up of each item.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999910216709543, \"rank\": 8.626394820711318e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you'd like to view this content, please adjust yourCookie Settings.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more about how we use cookies, please see ourCookie Guide.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the list of inclusions were water bottles, a toiletry bag, and a bespoke golden Samsung flip phone with an Olympic message engraved which Douglas unpacked in a later video.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"score\": 0.9156226920410117, \"rank\": 0.09205696304600827, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And of course, a supply of condoms were provided.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Displaying one blue and pink wrapper, cute messages emblazoned across the packaging caught the athlete's eye.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the field of love, play fair (ask for consent)\\\", one read.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The other insisted, \\\"No need to be a gold medallist to wear it!\\\"\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Garnering more than four million views, followers of the sailor had some questions.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have antisex beds but give condoms?\\ud83d\\ude2d\\\", one person asked.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love how they made anti-sex beds but still give u condoms bc they know it'll still happen,\\\" another joked.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Games chiefs toldSky Newsin March that they planned to reunite competitors following the COVID-induced intimacy ban that plagued the Tokyo Games, providing enough prophylactics for each athlete to get back on the horse twice a day.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Working with the athletes commission, we wanted to create some places where the athletes would feel very enthusiastic and comfortable,\\\" Laurent Michaud, director of the village told the publication.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Village is said to be the single most expensive project at the Paris Games at $3.3 billion - largely funded by property investors.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.1647717351924707e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Paris with love  The fast and the curious  Take notes  Take notes\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998381099, \"rank\": 1.6193038433118918e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}]}"